ll,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.\r\n\r\nNeither of these ports, indeed none of the lua libraries, currently provide package config files; so they are not easily found by cmake when they are installed.\r\n\r\nI suspect normally these dlls are not linked and simply loaded at runtime through lua's require command, but that doesn't work when a static triplet is used.\r\n\r\n### Proposed solution\r\n\r\nProvide package config files for these ports e.g. lpegConfig.cmake\r\n\r\n### Describe alternatives you've considered\r\n\r\nAlternatively I've considered restricting these packages to always build with dlls/so files even when a static triplet is chosen. I think it would be more valuable to support linking the libraries as this differentiates vcpkg from luarocks and results in simpler packaging.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nI am willing to work on the change myself if there is consensus.","closed_by":{"login":"vicroms","id":3526662,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjY2NjI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3526662?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms","html_url":"https://github.com/vicroms","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicroms/received_events","type":"Use